{"tid":2398874,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有對白鴿bb係屋企窗台出面 老母唔見左","createTime":"2021-02-07T16:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:58:51.000Z","uid":90670,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a36316a5e561c588447016722edbb4899f01ee42","tid":2398874,"uid":90670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n前排有對白鴿係我屋企窗台出面築巢 孵蛋<br />\n孵左兩隻bb出黎 <br />\n咁我屋企人話諗住等佢地孵完識飛就會走<br />\n我地日日都間唔中睇下佢地<br />\n<br />\n白鴿老豆老母每日都會輪班咁孵佢地 之後餵佢地<br />\n咁有一日我老母見到隻鴿老母腳好似跛下跛下咁 對翼好似甩左d毛咁<br />\n之後飛走左都冇理到啦<br />\n<br />\n正常白鴿老母日日夜晚都會返黎陪d bb<br />\n結果今日我成日都見唔到白鴿老豆老母<br />\n佢地係咪要棄子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係有咩不測<br />\n如果聽日之後都見唔到白鴿老豆老母<br />\n我應該要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acafedda91bc9e4d01eabcc8785762d86c73cd7b","tid":2398874,"uid":181318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"加餸"},{"pid":"5bbe990c7ecab6d4fbd37ec846507d5d3d8c495e","tid":2398874,"uid":117584,"like":48,"dislike":9,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEQrV9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEQrV9V.jpg&h=a29e2da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0afc6922e05cd3d5cde1fbd001593405e5df58eb","tid":2398874,"uid":31463,"like":7,"dislike":45,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"5bbe990c7ecab6d4fbd37ec846507d5d3d8c495e","tid":2398874,"uid":117584,"like":48,"dislike":9,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEQrV9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEQrV9V.jpg&h=a29e2da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"蝦蝦蝦 其實你係咪覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dde569f45333b575c2ae7f6bf45f97f2984b15","tid":2398874,"uid":90670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,